codex
The top-level `tevm` package is mostly re-export stubs, so API drift is the main risk: manifest exports, generated entrypoints, and TypeScript includes need to line up exactly. I’ve already found one likely JSR export drift and I’m checking whether the npm-facing barrels have similar mismatches before writing it up.
